'''第73届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2000年电影|2000年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2001年3月25日下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上20点30分）在美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的神殿礼堂举行，共计颁发了23座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[奥斯卡金像奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过{{lang|en|[[美国广播公司|ABC]]}}在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由吉尔·凯茨担任制片人，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨导演<ref>{{cite news | title = 73rd Annual Academy Awards | url = http://www.nytimes.com/tv/show/38935/73rd-Annual-Academy-Awards/details | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger Jr. | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150614220236/http://www.nytimes.com/tv/show/38935/73rd-Annual-Academy-Awards/details | archivedate = 2015-06-14}}</ref>，男演员[[史提夫·马丁|史提夫·马丁]]首次担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | title = Steve Martin To Host Oscars | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/steve-martin-to-host-oscars/ | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | publisher = CBS News (CBS Corporation) | date = 2001-12-19 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402170237/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/steve-martin-to-host-oscars/}}</ref>。3周前的3月3日，女演员[[蕾妮·齐薇格|蕾妮·齐薇格]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利威尔希尔饭店|比佛利威尔希尔丽晶酒店]]主持颁发[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Watch: 'Betty's' Zellweger to present Sci-Tech kudos | url = http://variety.com/2001/film/news/oscar-watch-182-1117794450/ | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | work = Variety | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616115325/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/oscar-watch-182-1117794450/ | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2001-02-27 | archivedate = 2015-06-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[角斗士_(电影)|角斗士]]》赢得包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]在内的5项大奖，是这个夜晚的最大赢家<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Rickey | first1 = Carrie | title = Oscar triumphs for Roberts, 'Gladiator' The Roman epic and its star, Russell Crowe, both won awards. Julia Roberts took best-actress honors, for "Erin Brockovich." | url = http://articles.philly.com/2001-03-26/news/25328541_1_visual-effects-picture-and-actor-statuettes | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222453/http://articles.philly.com/2001-03-26/news/25328541_1_visual-effects-picture-and-actor-statuettes | deadurl = no }}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括胜出4项的《[[臥虎藏龍_(電影)|卧虎藏龙]]》和《[[毒品网络|毒品网络]]》，以及获奖1项的《[[成名在望|几近成名]]》、《[[大妈_(电影)|大妈]]》（{{lang|en|''Big Mama''}}）、《[[永不妥协|永不妥协]]》、《[[父与女|父与女]]》、《[[鬼靈精_(2000年電影)|圣诞怪杰]]》、《[[战争存亡录|战争存亡录]]》（{{lang|en|''Into the Arms of Strangers: Stories of the Kindertransport''}}）、《[[波洛克_(电影)|波洛克]]》、《[[意欲成为|意欲成为]]》（{{lang|fr|''Quiero ser''}}）、《[[猎杀U-571|猎杀U-571]]》和《[[奇迹小子|奇迹小子]]》。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了近4300万美国观众收看。

== 获奖和提名 ==
2001年2月3日，[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]主席罗伯特·莱姆（{{lang|en|Robert Rehme}}）和曾获奥斯卡奖的女演员[[凯西·贝兹|凯西·贝兹]]一起公布第73届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单<ref>{{cite news|title=Academy announces Oscar nominations |url=http://cgi.cnn.com/2001/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/13/academy.awards/ |accessdate=2015-07-09 |publisher=CNN (Time Warner) |date=2001-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010529062641/http://cgi.cnn.com/2001/SHOWBIZ/Movies/02/13/academy.awards/ |archivedate=2001-05-29 }}</ref>。《[[角斗士_(电影)|角斗士]]》以12项提名领跑，《[[臥虎藏龍_(電影)|卧虎藏龙]]》以10项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Kaltenbach | first1 = Chris | title = It's Soderbergh vs. Soderbergh | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402092048/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2001-02-14/features/0102140292_1_gladiator-soderbergh-nominations | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | work = The Baltimore Sun | publisher = Timothy E. Ryan | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2001-02-14/features/0102140292_1_gladiator-soderbergh-nominations | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | date = 2001-02-14}}</ref>。

获奖名单在2001年3月25日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar spreads wealth | page = 1A | work = Tampa Bay Times | publisher = Times Publishing Company}}</ref>。《角斗士》成为1949年的《[[当代奸雄|当代奸雄]]》之后第一部没有赢得导演或编剧类奖项，但却夺得[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片奖]]的电影<ref name="Bona-2002">{{Citation | last = Bona | first = Damien | title = Inside Oscar 2 | year = 2002 | isbn = 0-345-44970-3 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Ballantine Books}}</ref>{{rp|374}}。[[史蒂文·索德伯格|史蒂文·索德伯格]]因《[[毒品网络|毒品网络]]》获[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演奖]]，还因《[[永不妥协|永不妥协]]》提名，成为历史上第3位在一年中获得两项导演奖提名的电影人{{ref label|Director|A|}}<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|351}}。《卧虎藏龙》是历史上第3部同年获最佳影片和[[奥斯卡最佳外语片奖|外语片奖]]的电影{{ref label|Foreign film|B|}}<ref name="Z">{{cite news|title=Gladiator Leads with 12 Oscar Nods |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706025632/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=109596 |deadurl=no |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=109596 |accessdate=2015-07-09 |publisher=ABC News (The Walt Disney Company) |date=2001-02-13 |archivedate=2015-07-06 }}</ref>，并且10项提名也创下非英语电影提名数量的新纪录<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|407}}，获奖4项则与《[[芬妮和亚历山大|芬妮和亚历山大]]》并列成为[[获奥斯卡金像奖的非英语电影|历史上获奖最多的非英语电影]]<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Hayes | first1 = Dade | title = ‘Tiger’ earns Oscar stripes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150208103709/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/tiger-earns-oscar-stripes-1117795962/ | url = https://variety.com/2001/film/news/tiger-earns-oscar-stripes-1117795962/ | accessdate = 2015-07-09 | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2001-03-25 | archivedate = 2015-02-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[杰昆·菲尼克斯|杰昆·菲尼克斯]]因《角斗士》获[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角奖]]提名，他的哥哥[[瑞凡·菲尼克斯|瑞凡·菲尼克斯]]曾因1988年的《[[不设限通缉|不设限通缉]]》（{{lang|en|''Running on Empty''}}）获同一奖项提名，两人也是史上第一对获该奖项提名的兄弟<ref>{{Citation | last = Crouse | first = Richard | title = Reel Winners: Movie Award Trivia | year = 2005 | isbn = 1-550-02574-0 | location = Toronto, Canada | publisher = Dundurn Press | page = 54}}</ref>。

