== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Steve_Martin_2011.jpg|130px]]担任第73届奥斯卡颁奖典礼主持人]]

虽然[[第72届奥斯卡金像奖|上届颁奖典礼]]获得评论界赞誉，收视率也有上涨，但[[比利·克里斯托|比利·克里斯托]]宣布无意连续担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | title = Crystal clear: He’s not up for Oscars | archivedate = 2015-06-16 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2000-12-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616114737/https://variety.com/2000/tv/news/crystal-clear-he-s-not-up-for-oscars-1117790195/ | url = https://variety.com/2000/tv/news/crystal-clear-he-s-not-up-for-oscars-1117790195/}}</ref>，因为需要出演电影《[[美国甜心|美国甜心]]》（{{lang|en|''America's Sweethearts''}}），还需要执导并制作[[电视电影|电视电影]]《[[职棒双雄|职棒双雄]]》（{{lang|en|''61*''}}）<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Armstrong | first1 = Mark | title = Oscar Gets Martinized! | archivedate = 2015-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150617132622/http://www.eonline.com/news/40888/oscars-get-martin-ized | deadurl = no | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/40888/oscars-get-martin-ized | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | publisher = E! (NBCUniversal) | date = 2000-12-18}}</ref>。吉尔·凯茨成为电视转播节目制作人后不久就聘请男演员兼笑匠[[史提夫·马丁|史提夫·马丁]]出任本届晚会主持人<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Munoz | first1 = Lorena | title = Martin Will Host Oscars, Saying, 'If You Can't Win 'Em, Join 'Em' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616165530/http://articles.latimes.com/2000/dec/19/entertainment/ca-1772 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2000/dec/19/entertainment/ca-1772 | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2000-12-19 | archivedate = 2015-06-16}}</ref>，凯茨对此表示：“他是电影明星，他既风趣又优雅，还有文化造谐——他会是位了不起的主持人”<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|343}}。美国电影艺术与科学学院主席罗伯特·莱姆也赞同凯茨的人选，称：“史蒂夫是个很有格调的人。我很高兴能够有他加入。他是我们的最佳人选之一，并且也接受了邀请，事情就这么简单。”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Feiwell | first1 = Jill | title = The Oscar Gig Goes to... | url = http://variety.com/2000/film/news/the-oscar-gig-goes-to-1117790716/ | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2000-12-17 | archivedate = 2015-06-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616114643/http://variety.com/2000/film/news/the-oscar-gig-goes-to-1117790716/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。马丁本人表示乐于担当主持之责，笑称既然没法得奖，那就加入到其行列之中<ref>{{cite news | title = Steve Martin To Host Academy Awards | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | work = Chicago Tribune | publisher = Tony W. Hunter | date = 2000-12-19 | archivedate = 2015-06-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150604205826/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2000-12-19/news/0012200031_1_73rd-academy-awards-oscar-nominations-steve-martin | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2000-12-19/news/0012200031_1_73rd-academy-awards-oscar-nominations-steve-martin}}</ref>。

凯茨为晚会定下主题，向[[斯坦利·库布里克|斯坦利·库布里克]]导演的科幻电影《[[2001太空漫游_(电影)|2001太空漫游]]》致敬<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Goddard | first1 = Peter | title = The show's other Best Director ; Louis J. Horvitz is the helmer behind the scenes | work = Toronto Star | publisher = Star Media Group | date = 2001-03-25| page = 10}}</ref>。为配合主题，正在执行[[远征2|远征2]]号航天任务进驻[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]的宇航员苏珊·赫尔姆斯（{{lang|en|Susan J. Helms}}）、尤里·尤萨科夫（{{lang|en|Yury Usachov}}）和詹姆斯·沃斯（{{lang|en|James S. Voss}}）在晚会开始时通过卫星连线介绍主持人马丁出场<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Jacobs | first1 = Bob | title = Oscars Go Global with International Introduction from Space | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150613230347/http://spaceflight.nasa.gov/spacenews/releases/2001/H01-55.html | archivedate = 2015-06-13 | url = http://spaceflight.nasa.gov/spacenews/releases/2001/H01-55.html | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | publisher = National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) | date = 2001-03-26}}</ref>。晚会期间，电影配乐家比尔·康堤（{{lang|en|Bill Conti}}）指挥管弦乐团演奏巴西爵士音乐家[[犹米勒·德奥达托|犹米勒·德奥达托]]（{{lang|en|Eumir Deodato}}）创作的混音版《查拉图斯特拉如是说》<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|366}}。此外，《2001太空漫游》的[[2001太空漫游_(小说)|原著小说]]作者[[亚瑟·查理斯·克拉克|亚瑟·查理斯·克拉克]]还在位于[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]的家中连线颁发原著改编奖<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|373}}<ref name="Pond-2005">{{Citation | last = Pond | first = Steve | title = The Big Show: High Times and Dirty Dealings Backstage at the Academy Awards | year = 2005 | isbn = 0-571-21193-3 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Faber and Faber}}</ref>{{rp|280}}。

另外还有多人参与颁奖典礼的制作。艺术指导设计师罗伊·克里斯托弗（{{lang|en|Roy Christopher}}）为晚会设计新舞台，其特点在于舞台地板到天花板通过观众席的后台墙壁形成类似百叶窗的巨大弧形，有媒体出版物认为这样的设计类似[[航天舱|航天舱]]的横截面<ref name="Set2001">{{cite news | last1 = Wethington | first1 = Jessica | title = Christopher’s sets set his work apart | url = http://variety.com/2001/film/news/christopher-s-sets-set-his-work-apart-1117794654/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616115221/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/christopher-s-sets-set-his-work-apart-1117794654/ | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2001-02-28 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-06-16}}</ref>。此外，舞台前后各有4道带有奥斯卡小金人轮廓的[[不锈钢|不锈钢]]弧形装饰，颁奖嘉宾和获奖者会从中穿过<ref name="Set2001" />。原创歌曲奖提名作品的现场表演由舞蹈家[[黛比·艾伦|黛比·艾伦]]编排<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Cruz | first1 = Clarissa | title = Puh-leeze, Academy | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = Entertainment Weekly | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2001/03/07/how-have-wild-and-crazy-oscar-telecast | publisher = Time Inc. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150712033939/http://www.ew.com/article/2001/03/07/how-have-wild-and-crazy-oscar-telecast | archivedate = 2015-07-12 | deadurl = no | date = 2001-03-07}}</ref>。音乐家[[马友友|马友友]]和[[伊扎克·帕尔曼|伊扎克·帕尔曼]]在舞台上表演5部原创配乐奖提名作品的音乐片段<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|370}}<ref name="Pond-2005" />{{rp|276}}。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截至2月13日提名公布时，全部5部获最佳影片奖提名电影的总计[[票房|票房]]收入为4亿7125万零742美元，平均每部9425万零148美元<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars">{{cite news | title = 2000 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2000&view=fulldetail&p=.htm | accessdate = 2015-07-11 | publisher = Box Office Mojo (Amazon.com) | archivedate = 2015-07-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150711160009/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2000&view=fulldetail&p=.htm}}</ref>。其中《角斗士》以1亿8661万零52美元位居榜首，其后分别是收入1亿2559万5205美元的《永不妥协》、进账7120万8084美元的《毒品网络》、收入4548万7799美元的《卧虎藏龙》和进账2707万1662美元的《浓情巧克力》<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars" />。

在2000年美国电影票房50强中，有15部电影获得共计49项提名。其中《荒岛余生》（季军）、《角斗士》（第4名）、《永不妥协》（第12名）、《毒品网络》（第31名）和《卧虎藏龙》（第41名）有获得最佳影片、导演或是任意一项演员、编剧类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite news | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705234153/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2001-02-12&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2000&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | title = 2000 Domestic Grosses | publisher = Box Office Mojo (Amazon.com) | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2001-02-12&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2000&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm}}</ref>。另外10部获提名的电影分别是《圣诞怪杰》（冠军）、《完美风暴》（第5名）、《拜见岳父大人》（第7名）、《爱国者》（第17名）、《太空牛仔》（第23名）、《变身国王》（第25名）、《猎杀U-571》（第26名）、《透明人》（第30名）、《102真狗》（第38名）和《入侵脑细胞》（第40名）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本场晚会获得大部分媒体的正面评价。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》电视评论员[[肯·塔克|肯·塔克]]（{{lang|en|Ken Tucker}}）称赞马丁的主持表现，称他低调而得体，表现挥洒自如，让整个夜晚的节目都有适当的节拍。在他看来，晚会的格调变化圆润自如，从[[吉恩·文森特|吉恩·文森特]]的摇滚乐风格和谐地切换到鲍勃·迪伦的原创歌曲表演。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Tucker | first1 = Ken | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no | title = Act 2 of the Oscars: The Show | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2001/04/06/act-2-oscars-show | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Inc. | date = 2000-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205051212/http://www.ew.com/article/2001/04/06/act-2-oscars-show}}</ref>。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》评论员罗伯特·比安卡（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）对节目的总体评价为中等，但特别称赞主持人马丁，以完全不同于比利·克里斯托的方式带来同等程度的幽默。“克里斯托非常努力地用良好的幽默感取悦你，而看起来面无表情的马丁则在扮猪吃老虎，用更厉害的笑话偷袭你。”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Bianco | first1 = Robert | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205075903/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/oscar2001/2001-03-26-steve-martin.htm#more | title = Martin's drollery keeps fast-moving Oscars on track | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2001-03-26 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/oscar2001/2001-03-26-steve-martin.htm#more}}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）认为，马丁是继“[[约翰尼·卡森|约翰尼·卡森]]之后最出众的奥斯卡主持”，他还称，节目本身似乎略显凝重，但即使是在那些显得崇高或是自命不凡的时刻，晚会也令人感到兴奋点十足<ref>{{cite news | last = Shales | first = Tom | title = With Our Favorite Maritn, Our Oscars Are a Class | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205010715/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A57782-2001Mar26.html | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A57782-2001Mar26.html | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = The Washington Post | publisher = Fred Ryan | date = 2001-03-27 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

部分媒体对节目的看法更为负面。《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的巴里·嘉隆（{{lang|en|Barry Garron}}）认为，晚会虽出自资深制作人吉尔·凯茨之手，并且持续时长也在计划范围内，但仍然显得过于漫长。他还取笑颁奖典礼中“大部分奖项都让观众提不起兴趣，但事实证明这样的节目仍然可以持续3个半小时。”<ref name="Bona-2002" />{{rp|382}}《[[亚特兰大宪法报|亚特兰大宪法报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Atlanta Journal-Constitution''}}）专栏作家史蒂夫·默里（{{lang|en|Steve Murray}}）称，主持人马丁缺少比利·克里斯托拥有的俏皮和个人魅力，也没有[[乌比·戈德堡|乌比·戈德堡]]那种催眠般的可怕自我满足，但即便不考虑这点，第73届奥斯卡颁奖典礼虽然是多年来持续时间最短的一届，但仍然显得没完没了<ref>{{cite news | last = Murray | first = Steve | title = They came, we saw, we conked out 'Gladiator,' 'Tiger,' 'Traffic' shared honors in snoozer of a show | work = The Atlanta Journal-Constitution | publisher = Cox Enterprises | date = 2001-03-26 | page = C1}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》电视评论员约翰·卡曼（{{lang|en|John Carman}}）表示，虽然是让史提夫·马丁这样的新手来主持，但奥斯卡颁奖典礼仍然将太多时间花在各种客套和礼貌上，真正有气魄的内容太少<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Carman | first1 = John | title = Quick But Dull / Disappointing lack of gaffes, tears during shorter show | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150619222031/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Quick-But-Dull-Disappointing-lack-of-gaffes-2938260.php | work = San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Jeffrey M. Johnson | archivedate = 2015-06-19 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Quick-But-Dull-Disappointing-lack-of-gaffes-2938260.php | date = 2001-03-26 | accessdate = 2015-07-12}}</ref>。

=== 收视率和获奖 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有4290万观众收看，与[[第72届奥斯卡金像奖|前一年]]相比降低了7%<ref>{{cite news | last = Carter | first = Bill | title = ABC Strikes Gold With the Oscars | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708075323/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/03/27/movies/and-the-loser-is-abc-an-all-time-low-for-viewers.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2001/03/27/movies/and-the-loser-is-abc-an-all-time-low-for-viewers.html | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger Jr. | date = 2001-03-27 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-08}}</ref><ref name="LA Times">{{cite news | last1 = Lowry | first1 = Brian | title = Awards Show's Ratings Slip, Early Figures Show | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2001/mar/27/entertainment/ca-43109 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616165552/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/mar/27/entertainment/ca-43109 | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2001-03-27 | archivedate = 2015-06-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，估计曾观看部分时段节目的观众总数有7220万<ref name="LA Times" />。从尼尔森收视率调查的数据看，节目的表现也不及前一年，吸引了26.2%的家庭收看，收视率超过40%<ref name="TVB Oscars">{{cite news|title=Academy Awards ratings |work=Television Bureau of Advertising |format=PDF |archivedate=2013-10-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016061652/http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |accessdate=2014-05-16 |url=http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外节目还在18至49岁年龄段人群中收获了17.8%的收视率<ref name="TVB Oscars" />。

2001年7月，颁奖典礼获得第53届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的8项提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Primetime Emmy Award database | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/73rd-annual-academy-awards | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | publisher = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences (ATAS) | archivedate = 2015-06-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150614051420/http://www.emmys.com/shows/73rd-annual-academy-awards}}</ref>，并在两个月后赢得综艺、音乐或特别节目类最佳音效奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Braxton | first = Greg | title = The Winners in Creative Arts Fields | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2001/nov/05/entertainment/ca-498 | accessdate = 2015-07-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616165559/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/nov/05/entertainment/ca-498 | deadurl = no | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2001-11-05 | archivedate = 2015-06-16}}</ref>。

